Package: BIKEgait
Type: Package
Title: Gait Event Detection Through Native Python Bridge
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Frederic", "Fer", email = "f.fer@institut-myologie.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Cross-language wrapper for BIKEgait native-accelerated gait event detection.
 The package calls the Python module 'BIKEgait' through 'reticulate'
 and exposes method selection and event detection from structured frames.
